00:27:53,356 --> 00:27:54,526
So we are getting


667
00:27:54,526 --> 00:27:56,106
to panGestureRecognizer
from the ScrollView.


668
00:27:56,106 --> 00:27:57,346
And we are telling it that we'd


669
00:27:57,346 --> 00:27:58,626
like to listen for
indirect touches.


