00:34:12,795 --> 00:34:15,686
And you can use some API
that's on UIResponder


817
00:34:15,686 --> 00:34:17,136
that you might recognize
from iOS.


818
00:34:17,136 --> 00:34:19,056
There is the inputAccessoryView


